# Week 5 Task 5 — Final Computer Vision Application

## Objective
Creating a complete computer vision application capable of detecting bottles automatically using a custom-trained YOLO model.

## Work Completed
- Created custom dataset
- Annotated images using Label Studio
- Resized images using FFmpeg
- Trained YOLO model
- Performed object detection on test images
- Generated final prediction outputs
- Created demo video with background audio

## Final Application
Bottle detection system capable of identifying bottles from unseen images and videos using trained YOLO weights.

## Technologies Used
- YOLO
- Ultralytics
- FFmpeg
- Label Studio

## Output
- Detection images with bounding boxes
- Final demo video with audio

## Outcome
Successfully completed an end-to-end computer vision workflow including:
- dataset preparation
- annotation
- preprocessing
- model training
- prediction
- demo generation
